sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE as Web Frontend
    participant API as Backend API
    participant Auth as Auth & Access Control
    participant Job as Job Service
    participant Queue as Queue & Scheduler
    participant Log as Log & Progress Service
    participant Artifact as Artifact Service
    participant DB as Database

    User->>FE: Login
    FE->>API: POST /auth/login
    API->>Auth: Validate company credentials
    Auth->>DB: Load user and role
    DB-->>Auth: User profile
    Auth-->>API: Session / token
    API-->>FE: Authenticated

    FE->>API: GET /projects
    API->>Auth: Filter projects by ownership / role
    Auth->>DB: Query authorized projects
    DB-->>API: Project list
    API-->>FE: Projects

    User->>FE: Start Training
    FE->>API: POST /projects/{project_id}/jobs
    API->>Auth: Authorize project action
    API->>Job: Validate project and config snapshot
    Job->>DB: Create job and snapshot records
    Job->>Queue: Enqueue job
    Queue->>DB: Persist queue entry
    API-->>FE: Job ID and status

    FE->>API: GET /jobs/{job_id}/status
    API->>DB: Load job state
    DB-->>API: Status and progress
    API-->>FE: Job status

    FE->>API: WebSocket connect /ws/jobs/{job_id}
    API->>Auth: Authorize stream access
    API->>Log: Subscribe to job stream
    Log-->>FE: Push log, progress, and status events

    FE->>API: GET /jobs/{job_id}/artifacts
    API->>Auth: Authorize artifact access
    API->>Artifact: List artifacts
    Artifact->>DB: Query registered artifacts
    DB-->>Artifact: Artifact metadata
    API-->>FE: Artifact list
